f="https://www.thivien.net/T%C6%B0-M%C3%A3-T%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Nh%C6%B0/author-HC1oHxsir20vL_KcVXiEhQ">Tư Mã Tương Như</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/T%C3%BAc-T%E1%BA%A1c-Th%E1%BA%A1ch-ph%E1%BB%91/poem-PbAyR9hrnDlU5BYc_nMPhg">Túc Tạc Thạch phố - 宿鑿石浦</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/T%E1%BB%A9-t%C3%B9ng/poem-gGXMjqTTUrdwriPEB0cMQw">Tứ tùng - 四松</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Ho%C3%A0ng-Ng%C3%B4n/T%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-nh%E1%BA%ADp-V%C5%A9-L%C3%A2m/poem-zIl4M0dW-cJ7FZYHgbDbWQ">Tương nhập Vũ Lâm - 將入武林</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Ho%C3%A0ng-Ng%C3%B4n/author-WFjodIEbfpQ-bFm4Fw6OTA">Trương Hoàng Ngôn</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
